The purpose of this is to give you a better understanding of how the #KMC BetaSeries controller works.
KMC BetaSeries itself is a micro game controller developed based on ST microcontroller, which is undoubtedly an excellent choice for many players, it has the characteristics of low cost, no delay, many functions and strong expansion
