KMC BetaSeries v1.2 features:

Real-time synchronous light switch
Real-time synchronous retarder switch
Real-time synchronous wiper switch
Real-time synchronous ignition switch
Design of wire harness separation
The compact case has 30 functions
Complete customization of functions
Synchronization of the lighting system
Strong compatibility for player custom devices
Functional compatibility of multiple games
Support for subsequent firmware updates
After-sales commissioning service
Pure aluminum alloy housing

ETS's "AUTO HOLD" automatic parking system is the only one in the whole network!




Significance of developing KMC BetaSeries v1.2:

In the future, all players' own creative needs only need to buy the switches, knobs and other physical switches they want to directly access the control and can be, there is no need to pay the cost of the controller, and there is no controller occupying too much USB port and UID conflict.
It can also be understood as a function, very complete and powerful JoyStick master control system, integrated modular design, when you want to switch between racing games and European truck simulator, you can directly pull the knob ignition switch from the controller, access the one button to start the ignition switch without program Settings, directly switch.



